        {
            "title": "限制出海｜發改委禁止Meta收購 央視批Manus規避監管 中國政府並非限制AI企業出海",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"630\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/esVXZlA2tbKYGpTHlG98Vg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/3af2387856d076b98b2a1a536cf760c3\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國家發改委早前禁止美國科技巨頭Meta投資人工智能(AI)初創企業<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Manus\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Manus;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Manus\">Manus</a>，央視社交媒體早前發表評論文章，指禁止收購主要與Manus遷冊逃避監管有關，並不是限制內地AI企業出海，反而今次事例提供更明確的監管參考。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">文章指出，Manus早期團隊、數據和研發主要都在中國，但從去年四月起Manus開始裁減中國員工，並將核心團隊和總部遷冊至新加坡。文章表示在中國孵化企業、其後遷冊到海外並被國際巨頭收購，對於這種規避監管的行為，國家主管機關當然需要介入。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-011b2e1b-7eed-3d3f-9072-d113ab5056f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">文章重申，近年不少中國企業「出海」，在海外設置分公司或者作為國際總部開展業務，國家從來未有禁止任何海外投資或者交易。但Manus主要在中國孵化，後來試圖遷冊令自己成為新加坡公司，規避了中國的監管規定，則觸碰到監管部門的底線。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">文章引述中國《外商投資安全審查辦法》第四條對審查範圍有較明確規定，指出Manus的通用AI智能體落入重要資訊科技與網路產品與服務、關鍵科技領域；若果外資提出全面收購，Manus本應主動申報；若收購後核心技術和團隊將完整轉移至境外，更需要在國家安全風險層面進行申報和評估。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%B7-%E7%99%BC%E6%94%B9%E5%A7%94%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2meta%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E6%89%B9manus%E8%A6%8F%E9%81%BF%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%A6%E9%9D%9E%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6ai%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%B7-050909755.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 13:20:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "奶茶股狂飆10%，年內近乎翻倍！Warren AI亮\"估值紅燈\"",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nxPpFXPmPXGhujCjzaDxTQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC4H0HF_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月30日，奶茶股滬上阿姨 (HK:2589)盤中大升10%，年內股價接近翻倍！</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"590\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/B6HHscrjmXtN.OEXVPX1tQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/2e3e885fa5b810e0fae94b999c6f55b8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Warren AI分析指出，滬上阿姨已進入「高增長-高估值-高波動」三高階段，短線仍有交易機會，但需防範高位回撤風險。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>消息面：業績與擴張雙輪驅動</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>2025</strong><strong>年營收同比增長</strong><strong>36%</strong><strong>至</strong><strong>44.66</strong><strong>億人民幣，淨利潤同比大增</strong><strong>52.4%</strong><strong>至</strong><strong>5.01</strong><strong>億人民幣。</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">門店總數達11,449家，較上年增長24.8%，已突破1萬家大關，反映門店擴張持續強勁。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">券商預測2026-2028年淨利將分別達6.7/7.8/9.0億人民幣，維持「買入」評級，2026年給予15倍PE，並測算合理價值108.28港元/股。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滬上阿姨印尼首店落地雅加達高端商圈 Emporium Pluit Mall，開業人氣火爆，前三日日均銷量近1500杯。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>技術面：極端強勢，風險同步抬升</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>近期單日升幅超</strong><strong>12%</strong><strong>，年內累計升幅接近翻倍，技術形態處於加速上升階段。</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">短線成交量急劇放大，主力資金活躍，動能極強。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但已出現多次大陽線拉升，短期技術指標臨近超買，波動性顯著提升。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以「放量突破」、「平台整理後加速」為典型結構，後續需關注資金面持續性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>估值分析：估值高位，風險升溫</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2026年預測PE為15倍，券商給予目標價空間約23%（由88.2港元至108.28港元）。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當前P/E達22.0x，PEG 0.79，遠高於行業均值，回撤風險突出。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">需警惕擴張放緩、單店收益波動等潛在風險因素，滬上阿姨2025年關閉門店1,383家，閉店率12.11%，為同業最高。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">券商對滬上阿姨的看法存在明顯分歧，看多派以銀河證券、廣發證券為代表，核心邏輯是多品牌矩陣加速擴張疊加咖啡+早餐場景增量；海通國際則下調至\"中性\"，直指閉店率高企及補貼退坡風險。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>5</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股即將上線！依家訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>，<span>唔好錯過啦！</span></span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/c8btmIWRGCFYTTfPcn2L3g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/55c306ced78e7aede67eacacd53f9e49\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leadi